current_prompt_text:
Break the problem into a maximum of 2 focused subproblems for other agents. Each helper must receive a single, distinct task (e.g., strategy design or implementation logic) to avoid overlap. Use plain text only inside helper instructions; do not use markdown, code fences, or LaTeX. 

Your entire response must be a single, valid JSON object. Do not include any text, markdown formatting, or code fences before or after the JSON object.

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}

